headline.print_headline: Alibaba Stock Soars in Jubilant Trading Debut
headline.main: Alibaba Stock Soars in Jubilant Trading Debut

lead_paragraph: Alibaba debuted as a publicly traded company Friday and swiftly climbed nearly 40 percent in a mammoth IPO that offered eager investors seemingly unlimited growth potential and a way to tap into the burgeoning Chinese middle class.
